text: The SAAB S-100 is a Swedish military aircraft. It is designed to be an AWACS aircraft. It was built from the SAAB 340's airliner. Ukraine got (2025) an [ Argus radar airplane or Saab radar airplane or] Saab 340 AEW&C.; It is an Airborne early warning and control (picture) airplane. Militaries that use these airplanes: Ukraine is using its first Saab 340 AEW&C; It got it in 2025. == Bibliography == * == References == Category:Military aircraft Category:Swedish military aircraft Category:Transport in Sweden
